Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:05.90,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然如此还是一定有弱小的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:09.31,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就保护他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.75,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这才能表现我们的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:19.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.30,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强者出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:32.70,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从今天起我最酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:38.84,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}崭新的最强的NO.1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.70,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:48.79,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}的确从今天起 我就是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:14.12,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夢ならあるはずだ　あなたにも僕にでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:14.12,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都有梦想 你我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:22.40,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見つかりにくいだけだ忙しすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:22.40,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但因为太忙而很难被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:34.69,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ミエナイチカラで　だれもが強く繋がっている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:34.69,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}谁都被看不到的力量强力的连接着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:39.82,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何も大したことじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:39.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:44.54,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいても離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:44.54,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论是否在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:49.35,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨日　今日　明日と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:49.35,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天 今天 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:22:02.26,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔のあなたはいつでも　この胸にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:22:02.26,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑容永远深印在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.92,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You've got to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:09.41,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's never too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.39,Default3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I never say die
